22 (a) "Capital gains increment" is the difference between:
23 (i) the current calendar year's capital gains estimate as described in the most recent official
24 revenue estimate provided for in 5-5-227; and
25 (ii) the lowest reported capital gains income from any year within the most recent 10 years of
26 available data, as published in the department of revenue's biennial report provided for in 15-1-205.
